import Navbar from "./Navbar"
import Home from "./pages/Home"
import inventory from "./pages/inventory"
import rooms from "./pages/rooms"
import services from "./pages/services"



function App() {
  let component
  switch (window.location.pathname) {
    case "/":
      component=<Home />
      break

      case "/":
      component= <inventory/>
      break
      case "/rooms":
      component= <rooms/>
      break

      case "/services":
        component= <services/>
      break
  }
  return (
    <>
    <Navbar/>
    {component}
    </>


  )
}

export default App
